headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: Prices of dividend stocks tend to be less volatile than stocks that don't pay dividends.  Philip Morris International is well-positioned for continued growth.  Dominion Energy dividend at its current price yields 5%, and the utility is seeing rapid growth in demand from the data center market.
